-- Job Openings in U.S. Rose by 75,000 in August to 3.88 Million
-- B y   S h o b h a n a   C h a n d r a
-- 2013-10-24T14:03:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-24/job-openings-in-u-s-rose-by-75-000-in-august-to-3-88-million.html
The number of  positions  waiting to
be filled in the U.S. rose by 75,000 to 3.88 million in August
from a revised 3.81 million in the prior month, the Labor
Department reported today in  Washington . The pace of hiring was
little changed.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shobhana Chandra in Washington at 
 schandra1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
